column33: Warner Brothers: Keep Johnny Depp as Grindlewald
column34: They said Johnny Depp is not going to be Grindlewald no more! Why? You may ask. Well because he was a victim of domestic violence and Amber Heard was trying to beat him to the punch literally and didn’t want the world to know she was abusing Johnny Depp. This isn’t right! Why must we sit back and allow any company to take away one of our favorite actors because of someone trying to ruin his life and career. Your signing this petition to keep him in entertainment as all your favorite characters. Let’s get a million signatures of we can, but let’s keep our Johnny!
